const Settings = () => { document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => { const saveButton = document.querySelector(".save-button"); const confirmationMessage = document.getElementById( "confirmation-message" ); saveButton.addEventListener("click", () => { // Collect data from all forms const accountForm = document.getElementById("account-info-form"); const childForm = document.getElementById("child-info-form"); const notificationForm = document.getElementById( "notification-settings-form" ); const securityForm = document.getElementById( "security-settings-form" ); const accountData = new FormData(accountForm); const childData = new FormData(childForm); const notificationData = new FormData(notificationForm); const securityData = new FormData(securityForm); // Process or save data as needed // Example: Convert FormData to JSON or send to a server const data = { account: Object.fromEntries(accountData.entries()), child: Object.fromEntries(childData.entries()), notifications: Object.fromEntries(notificationData.entries()), security: Object.fromEntries(securityData.entries()), }; console.log(data); // Log the data or send it to a server // Show confirmation message confirmationMessage.textContent = "Your changes have been saved!"; }); }); return (
